as-vegas-sphere-3553209">最近又延长至 3 月</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phish">菲什</a>将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/phish-announced-as-the-next-sphere-residency-3552458">本月晚些时候进行为期一周的驻场演出，</a>而据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯</a>也参与了谈判。</p><p> <a href="https://nypost.com/2023/11/15/business/james-dolan-looks-to-land-beyonce-to-light-up-las-vegas-sphere-sources/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow"><em>《纽约邮报》</em></a>的另一篇报道暗示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bon-jovi">邦乔维</a>等人也“被考虑”参加驻场演出。</p><p>不过，报告中的内部人士也解释说，一些艺术家因在 Sphere 举办展览的成本而望而却步，由于其巨大的液晶环绕屏幕，该展览的费用尤其昂贵。 </p><figure id="attachment_3552185" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3552185" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3552185" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sphere@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2023 年 10 月 1 日，在美国内华达州拉斯维加斯的威尼斯度假村看到球体" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sphere@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sphere@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sphere@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sphere@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sphere@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sphere@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3552185" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年 10 月 1 日，在美国内华达州拉斯维加斯的威尼斯度假村看到该球体。图片来源：Tayfun Coskun/Anadolu Agency via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Dead &amp; Company 今年夏天开始了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dead-company-to-embark-on-final-tour-in-summer-2023-3316279">一场所谓的“告别”巡演</a>，但<a href="https://twitter.com/BobWeir/status/1573388982834053120" target="_blank" rel="noopener">威尔在 Twitter 上写道</a>：“好吧，看起来这套衣服就到此为止了；但别担心，我们都会以一种或另一种形式出现在那里，直到我们倒下……”</p><p> Word of Dead &amp; Company 解散的消息<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-weir-responds-to-reports-of-dead-company-retiring-from-touring-news-to-me-3202219">最早出现在今年早些时候</a>，当时<i>《滚石》杂志</i>在 4 月份推测 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dead-company-share-dates-for-2022-us-summer-tour-3201451">他们 22 年夏季的北美巡演</a>将是他们的最后一次。文章引用了“与 Dead &amp; Company 关系密切的消息人士”作为参考点，以及克罗伊茨曼<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bill-kreutzmann-pulls-out-of-dead-company-shows-in-mexico-on-doctors-orders-3129226">最近的健康问题</a>。然而，威尔很快否认了这些谣言，并在推特上表示，乐队的解散计划“对我来说是新闻”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dead-company-reportedly-in-talks-for-2024-las-vegas-sphere-residency-3559777">据报道，Dead &amp; Company 正在洽谈 2024 年拉斯维加斯球驻场项目的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
